      <title type="html">CSS Customizing</title>
      <link href="https://20-2-skku-oss.github.io/2020-2-OSS-11/csscustomizing" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="CSS Customizing" />
      <published>2020-12-07T00:00:00+09:00</published>
      <updated>2020-12-07T00:00:00+09:00</updated>
      <id>https://20-2-skku-oss.github.io/2020-2-OSS-11/csscustomizing</id>
      <content type="html" xml:base="https://20-2-skku-oss.github.io/2020-2-OSS-11/csscustomizing">&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;table-of-contents-list&quot;&gt;STATIC_PAGE 탭은 다음과 같이 구성되어 있습니다. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;table-of-contents-list&quot;&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;./staticpage-introduction&quot;&gt;Static Page Introduction&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;./csscustomizing&quot;&gt;CSS Customizing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;./staticpagecontents&quot;&gt;Static Page Contents&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;css-customizing&quot;&gt;CSS Customizing&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;UI를 보기 편하게 만들기위해 css customizing을 진행하였습니다. &lt;em&gt;custom.css&lt;/em&gt;를 편집하고 gulp를 이용하여 압축을 한 후에, 포스트의 설정을 
다루고 있는 &lt;em&gt;default.html&lt;/em&gt;에&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;language-html highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;c&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;!-- custom.css --&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;link&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;rel=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;stylesheet&quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;type=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;text/css&quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;href=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;/2020-2-OSS-11/assets/built/custom.css&quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;해당 코드를 삽입하여 css customizing을 완료하였습니다.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;한글-웹폰트-설정&quot;&gt;한글 웹폰트 설정&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;커스터마이징 이후에도 여전히 한글의 가독성이 떨어졌고, 이를 해결하기 위해 한글폰트를 나눔고딕 폰트로 
변경하였습니다. 나눔고딕 폰트를 &lt;em&gt;default.html&lt;/em&gt;에 추가하고,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;language-html highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;c&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;!-- 웹폰트 추가 --&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;link&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;rel=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;stylesheet&quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;href=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;https://fonts.googleapis.com/earlyaccess/nanumgothic.css&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;screen.css&lt;/em&gt; 파일에 ‘Nanum Gothic’을 추가해줌으로써,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;language-css highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nc&quot;&gt;.post-full-content&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nl&quot;&gt;position&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;relative&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nl&quot;&gt;margin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nl&quot;&gt;padding&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;70px&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;100px&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nl&quot;&gt;min-height&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;230px&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nl&quot;&gt;font-family&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;Georgia&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;'Nanum Gothic'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;serif&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nl&quot;&gt;font-size&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;2.2rem&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nl&quot;&gt;line-height&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;1.6em&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nl&quot;&gt;background&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;#fff&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;한글의 가독성을 향상시켰습니다.&lt;/p&gt;</content>

      
      
      
      
      

